You are analyzing code for **Insecure Default Configuration** vulnerabilities.

## What Are Insecure Defaults?

Insecure defaults occur when an application ships with security-relevant settings set to permissive or debug values, and those values are not overridden in production. This includes disabled security flags (secure cookies set to false, CSRF protection off), debug mode in production, wildcard CORS origins, verbose error reporting, and default credentials left unchanged.

